  "notes": "3rd great-grandfather on the Gordon line. Born in Ireland, 1789. Immigrant to America. Married Maria Mayhue on December 2, 1830 in Washington, DC. Four children, all born in Washington DC: Thomas H. (c. 1835), James H. (1837-1869), Elizabeth Ann (1840-1920), George M. (1848-1863). Son George died at 15 in 1863 during the Civil War era. Wife Maria died April 26, 1867. Son James died July 13, 1869. Death date unknown."
